<h1 align="center">hag</h1>
<h5 align="center">A Hotkey AGgregator.</h5>
<p align="center">
  <a href="https://github.com/loiccoyle/hag/actions/workflows/ci.yml"><img src="https://github.com/loiccoyle/hag/actions/workflows/ci.yml/badge.svg"></a>
